                  , jun. did receive and take into his possession one pound eleven shillings and sixpence, for and on account of his said master, and that he afterwards fraudulently and feloniously did embezzle, secrete, and steal the same
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Count. For like offence, only laying it to be the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050918-12-victim133" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Topham
                  <interp inst="t18050918-12-victim133" type="surname" value="Topham"></interp>
